(3, 1, 1, '', '2020-12-28 22:49:33', 595, 2637, 'e4a0e115066624f984bb1c9f347c26d334f09b6a', '{\"id\":1,\"asset_id\":\"61\",\"title\":\"Quem Somos\",\"alias\":\"quem-somos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Apaixonado por plantas, comecei a plantar mudas de Ip\\u00ea Amarelo que brotavam no jardim do meu pr\\u00e9dio. Usando caixas de leite e suco, garrafas de refrigerante e vasilhas de uvas fui tomando gosto pela fun\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hoje montamos um viveiro e estamos compartilhando as mudas com amigos e parentes, decidindo montar o projeto\\u00a0<strong>Muda pra Vida.\\u00a0<\\/strong>O Projeto vai cadastrar quem pegou as mudas, para registro da localiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da muda e fotos com a sua evolu\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Temos o objetivo de cadastrar mais fornecedores de mudas e ter variedades em outros lugares!<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As mudas hoje dispon\\u00edveis s\\u00e3o de Ip\\u00ea Amarelo e Pitangueiras, e estamos com mais de 300 mudas, principalmente que foram plantadas no per\\u00edodo da Pandemia.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2020-10-16 18:58:58\",\"created_by\":\"595\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-12-28 22:49:33\",\"modified_by\":\"595\",\"checked_out\":\"595\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-12-28 22:46:28\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-10-16 18:58:58\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/mudas_ipe.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"right\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Mudas de Ip\\\\u00ea\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":