(15, 2, 1, '', '2021-02-26 22:28:27', 595, 2540, 'e118c3cb931e27d75be5b8d2142fc1e3cb8c518c', '{\"id\":2,\"asset_id\":\"75\",\"title\":\"Ip\\u00ea-Amarelo\",\"alias\":\"ipe-amarelo\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O ip\\u00ea-amarelo, tamb\\u00e9m conhecido no Brasil como aip\\u00ea, ip\\u00ea-branco, ip\\u00ea-mamono, ip\\u00ea-mandioca, ip\\u00ea-ouro, ip\\u00ea-pardo, ip\\u00ea-vacariano, ip\\u00ea-tabaco, ip\\u00ea-do-cerrado, ip\\u00ea-dourado, ip\\u00ea-da-serra, ipezeiro, pau-d\\u2019arco-amarelo, taipoca ou apenas ip\\u00ea (nome cient\\u00edfico: Handroanthus albus) \\u00e9 uma \\u00e1rvore do g\\u00eanero Handroanthus.Pode atingir 30 metros de altura e 60 cent\\u00edmetros de di\\u00e2metro, e \\u00e9 caducif\\u00f3lia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"readmore\\\"><a href=\\\"index.php\\/arvores?view=species&amp;layout=default_item&amp;id=69\\\">Saiba mais...<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2020-12-28 23:35:14\",\"created_by\":\"595\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2021-02-26 22:28:27\",\"modified_by\":\"595\",\"checked_out\":\"595\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2021-02-26 22:27:26\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-12-28 23:35:14\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/produtos\\\\\\/ipe_amarelo_2.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"right\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"Ip\\\\u00ea Amarelo\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/produtos\\\\\\/ipe_amarelo_2.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"left\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Ip\\\\u00ea Amarelo\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"1\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(16, 1, 1, '', '2021-03-02 21:47:24', 595, 2812, '8b8c3a9e2814288912f39471c5da316a43b1c4bf', '{\"id\":1,\"asset_id\":\"61\",\"title\":\"Quem Somos\",\"alias\":\"quem-somos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Apaixonado por plantas, comecei a plantar mudas de Ip\\u00ea Amarelo que brotavam no jardim do meu pr\\u00e9dio, oriundas das sementes da matriz que temos na porta e l\\u00e1 caiam, naturalmente. Usando caixas de leite e suco, garrafas pets e embalagens descart\\u00e1veis, fui tomando gosto pela fun\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Hoje, montamos um viveiro e estamos compartilhando as mudas com amigos e parentes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>E, assim, nasceu a ideia de montar o Muda pra Vida! O Projeto vai cadastrar quem pegou as mudas, para registro da localiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o de onde a muda foi plantada e envio de fotos, para acompanharmos a sua evolu\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Hoje, temos dispon\\u00edveis, para doa\\u00e7\\u00e3o, mais de 300 mudas, entre Ip\\u00ea Amarelo e Pitangueira, a maioria plantada no per\\u00edodo da pandemia. O objetivo \\u00e9 cadastrarmos mais fornecedores que, assim como n\\u00f3s, desejem espalhar suas sementes, para ampliarmos a variedade e as op\\u00e7\\u00f5es de locais para retirada.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2020-10-16 18:58:58\",\"created_by\":\"595\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2021-03-02 21:47:24\",\"modified_by\":\"595\",\"checked_out\":\"595\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2021-03-02 21:47:06\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-10-16 18:58:58\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/mudas_ipe.jpg\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"right\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"Mudas de Ip\\\\u00ea\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"71\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);

